These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: cricket, lacrosse, parkour
1. Sport:lacrosse is on the right of Sport:parkour##1
2. Sport:cricket is on the far right##1
3. Sport:cricket is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | parkour | lacrosse | cricket |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: kiwi, spinach, plum
1. Food:spinach is in an odd position##4
2. Food:kiwi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | kiwi | plum | spinach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: card-games, gardening, sudoku
1. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left or right of Hobby:sudoku##3
3. Hobby:sudoku is on the right of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | gardening | sudoku |

 #################################
 
